name: TrainHorns
0:
”Alexa, open train horns”
”Alexa, play train horns”
”Alexa, ask train horns”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: train horns
des:
Now you too can experience life living near a railway. Use these train horns to wake up the kids, or when playing with their trains.

You can stop them with "Alexa stop", or "Alexa cancel" - you need the 'Alexa' prefix !
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
